description: It's no secret, if you're looking for the best pizza around you need wood-fired pizza, and at Furando's that's exactly what you'll get! Made hot and fresh from the best ingredients, every pizza from Furando's Wood Fired Pizza is guaranteed to be the very best you've ever had. Build your own or choose from one of their signature pies, you'll love everything on offer at Furando's!
name: Fundaro's Wood Fired Pizza
